act.js, Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, REST APIs, testing, debugging, and agile development.`,techBadges:[`React.js`,`Node.js`,`MongoDB`,`Express.js`,`Python`,`JavaScript`,`OpenCV`],stats:[{value:`4+`,label:`Months`,sublabel:`Industry Experience`},{value:`4+`,label:`Major`,sublabel:`Projects`},{value:`10+`,label:`Technologies`,sublabel:`Mastered`},{value:`1`,label:`Professional`,sublabel:`Internship`},{value:`100%`,label:`Passion for`,sublabel:`Building Software`}],aboutContent:`I am a Computer Science Engineering Graduate and Full Stack Web Developer with a strong passion for building modern web applications and solving real-world problems through technology. My expertise lies in MERN Stack development, RESTful API integration, responsive frontend design, backend architecture, database management, and software testing. During my internship at Prinston Smart Engineers, I worked on client-facing applications, collaborated with development teams, and contributed to delivering high-quality software solutions using industry-standard development practices. I am currently seeking opportunities where I can contribute as a Software Developer while continuously expanding my technical expertise.`,experience:{role:`Full Stack Web Developer (MERN Intern)`,company:`Prinston Smart Engineers`,duration:`January 2026 – May 2026`,location:`Bangalore, India`,responsibilities:[`Built and maintained responsive React.js user interfaces`,`Designed and implemented RESTful APIs using Node.js and Express.js`,`Worked closely with frontend and backend systems`,`Collaborated with a 4-member development team using Git and GitHub`,`Performed debugging, testing, and bug fixing`,`Contributed to reducing UI issues through systematic troubleshooting`,`Participated in Agile sprint planning and daily standups`,`Delivered assigned modules within sprint deadlines`]},projects:[{id:1,title:`Home Cleaning Services Booking Portal`,techStack:`MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js`,description:`A complete MERN-based service booking platform with role-based access control, secure authentication, scheduling management, and administrative dashboards.`,features:[`JWT Authentication`,`Role-Based Access`,`Real-Time Booking Management`,`Admin Dashboard`,`Service Tracking`],imageSeq:`project-cleaning-01`},{id:2,title:`Driver Drowsiness Detection System`,techStack:`Python, OpenCV, Keras, TensorFlow`,description:`An AI-powered computer vision system that monitors driver alertness using eye movement and facial analysis to prevent accidents.`,features:[`Real-Time Detection`,`92% Accuracy`,`Audio Alert System`,`CNN-Based Model`,`Computer Vision Processing`],imageSeq:`project-drowsiness-02`},{id:3,title:`Voice Based Email System`,techStack:`Python, SpeechRecognition, pyttsx3, SMTP`,description:`An accessibility-focused email application enabling visually impaired users to send, read, and manage emails using voice commands.`,features:[`Speech-to-Text`,`Text-to-Speech`,`Voice Navigation`,`Accessibility First Design`],imageSeq:`project-voice-03`},{id:4,title:`Luxe Cafe Website`,techStack:`HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript`,description:`A luxury-themed responsive café website featuring smooth animations, modern UI design, and performance optimization.`,features:[`Responsive Design`,`Animation Effects`,`Fast Loading`,`Premium UI`],imageSeq:`project-cafe-04`}],skills:{frontend:[`React.js`,`HTML5`,`CSS3`,`JavaScript`,`Responsive Design`],backend:[`Node.js`,`Express.js`,`REST APIs`,`JWT Authentication`],databases:[`MongoDB`,`MySQL`,`SQL`],languages:[`Python`,`JavaScript`,`C++`,`PHP`],ai:[`OpenCV`,`TensorFlow`,`Keras`,`Scikit-Learn`,`SpeechRecognition`],tools:[`Git`,`GitHub`,`VS Code`,`Postman`,`Eclipse`]},education:{degree:`Bachelor of Engineering`,field:`Computer Science Engineering`,institution:`T John Institute of Technology`,location:`Bangalore, Karnataka`,duration:`2022 – 2026`,status:`Graduated`},certifications:[{title:`Artificial Intelligence Implementation`,issuer:`Microsoft & SAP`},{title:`Mac